00:43:55.590 --> 00:43:57.420
and we met him there.

00:43:57.420 --> 00:43:58.740
He came.

00:43:58.740 --> 00:44:04.500
He entered the room like this
with his wife, you know, soft--

00:44:04.500 --> 00:44:06.590
the spine, the hips, everything.

00:44:06.590 --> 00:44:08.880
He's like a 15-year-old.

00:44:08.880 --> 00:44:11.070
Like a ballet
dancer he's walking.

00:44:11.070 --> 00:44:13.470
He's not like an 80-year-old.

00:44:13.470 --> 00:44:18.300
His wife, 80-something too, and
